Good visibility: greater than 5 miles (8 kilometers)
Moderate visibility: between 3 to 5 miles (5 to 8 kilometers)
Poor visibility: between 1 to 3 miles (1.6 to 5 kilometers)
Very poor visibility: between 0.5 to 1 mile (0.8 to 1.6 kilometers)
Near zero visibility: less than 0.5 miles (0.8 kilometers)